message.content: cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.SY, cs.MA, cs.ET - The paper discusses the use of Reinforcement Learning techniques for decision making in microgrids. This falls under the domain of Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI) and Machine Learning (cs.LG). The problem formulation involves multiple agents making decisions, which falls under the category of Multi-Agent Systems (cs.MA) and the use of Markov Decision Process (MDP) and Reinforcement Learning techniques falls under the category of Control Systems (cs.SY). Additionally, the paper discusses the use of batteries for storing renewable power, which falls under the category of Energy (cs.ET).
